      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW LINDEN (2) struggled in tougher grade last start after settling well back at this track, but prior to that won by a nose at Warrnambool (22.37) beating Starship Atlas in a Grade 5 on February 12. Form from his last run is proving strong. Key runner on his best form. ZIVA BALE (6) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (22.48) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Can feature with the right run. TOUCH OF SIN (1) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 6 last run (22.94) at Geelong. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Will give a great sight again. BOROUGH BANKER (4) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
